Usage: reportConnectivity [-help] <pinName> [-level <integer>] [-pinOnly]

-help                     # Prints out the command usage
<pinName>                 # specify pinName whose connectivity is to be
                          # reported (string, required)
-level <integer>          # Number of levels to be printed in the report.
                          # Default 1 (int, optional)
-pinOnly                  # consice report with partition pin and io pin will
                          # be printed (bool, optional)